70010000072408.description:
Welcome to the world of dizzying and adrenaline racing! In this game you will face the most dangerous obstacles at a great height. On your way you have to overcome various obstacles, avoid traps and set a new speed record on dangerous tracks.

The game has a huge selection of powerful sports cars. Win races, set new records and fill up your garage with powerful sports cars. And don't forget to upgrade your car to the maximum level!

On each track you will encounter unique obstacles that will try to knock you off the track. Some obstacles can suddenly change your direction of travel, others can stop your car if you are not careful and attentive.

Try to overcome as many obstacles as possible and set your new personal speed record on each track. Prove to everyone who is the King of the Downhill here!

GAME FEATURES:
• Excellent warm-up for dexterity and attentiveness;
• Lots of tracks with varying difficulty;
• Large garage of powerful sports cars;
• Addictive gameplay for all ages;
• Management with the Joy-Con™️ controllers;

70010000048756.description:
Prepare for cuteness overload, relentless training, and fierce rivalry as you and your hamsters take on challenges while traversing the maze, riding a skateboard, and more! Be the first to cross the finish line to earn rewards and yummy treats!

FEATURES:
- Experience fierce competition in a laid-back style – all you need is a single button, but don't think for one second that it means you won’t break a sweat!
- Race and compete with AI-driven hamsters or other players in multiplayer modes – compete with others, whether they're next to you, or hundreds of miles away;
- Develop your hamsters’ abilities and skillsets to compete against higher-level opponents;
- Look after your hamsters and expand their house – furnish it with new equipment and make it the mansion they deserve;
- Name your hamsters and customize them – there are over 100 cosmetic items!
- Enjoy detailed graphics and cute animations, no matter what mode you're playing!

70050000046138.description:
Spooky Hamster House DLC is the expansion pack for Hamster Playground – a fresh dash of content to enrich your experience! Our hamsters are keen on celebrating social events and they are more than ready to dip their paws into the foggy waters of unknown and scary.
Help them by redecorating their house in a spooky way and dressing them up in new costumes that would not be out of place at a zombie prom! Complete fresh quests and experience a new, deliciously witchy hamster job.

Spooky Hamster House DLC features:
new, spooky items for the hamster house;
new, scary costumes;
brand-new quests with unique rewards;
a super spooky job for your hamsters!

70010000080967.description:
The goal of the game is simple - deliver various cargo to the desired point and complete tasks. But be extremely careful - the load may be unstable and fragile!

The game has many different tasks with different levels of difficulty - from the simplest with light and small loads to complex with bulky and fragile loads.

Plunge into a real challenge for fans of work transport simulators and transport all the cargo!

GAME FEATURES:
- Realistic physics and forklift control system;
- Lots of different tasks;
- Many different types of cargo;
- Realistic sounds.

70010000081027.description:
The player finds himself in a mysterious maze. The player's goal is to find a way out of this dark place by solving riddles, collecting items and avoiding dangerous monsters lurking around every corner.

Players will explore labyrinthine corridors and rooms that constantly change and mysteriously take them to new places. Their lives will be threatened by various dangers, from monsters to traps and riddles that must be solved in order to move forward.

Risk, tension and an atmosphere of mystery pose a real challenge for fans of horror games.

GAME FEATURES:
• An escape simulator that constantly keeps you on your toes;
• Many labyrinths of varying complexity;
• Heartbreaking atmosphere of liminal spaces;
• Excellent warm-up for the mind and attentiveness.
